pedia.org/resource/International_Judo_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Judo_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Further investigations will be conducted to determine what happened.\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Guram Tushishvili lost to home favourite Teddy Riner|GETTYFrench Olympic Judoka Frederique Jossinet, speaking on Eurosport, slammed Tushishvili for his angry reaction on the mat.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2347, \"end\": 2364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guram_Tushishvili\", \"score\": 0.9999999754272725, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guram Tushishvili\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guram_Tushishvili\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guram_Tushishvili\"}, {\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teddy Riner\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teddy_Riner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In judo, values, respect for the opponent and the winner are very important,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His reaction was pitiful and not in keeping with the values of judo.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He got 'hansoku-make', a disqualification.\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can not have a reaction like that.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not judo.\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LATEST SPORT NEWS:Judy Murray makes demand over Imane Khelif controversy after Italian boxer quit fightTom Daley makes complaint about Olympic Village as diving star talks Andy Murray and Rafael Nadal encountersImane Khelif childhood snaps surface as gen